Package javax.xml.rpc.server

Interface Summary
ServiceLifecycle The javax.xml.rpc.server.ServiceLifecycle defines a lifecycle interface for a JAX-RPC service endpoint.
ServletEndpointContext The ServletEndpointContext provides an endpoint context maintained by the underlying servlet container based JAX-RPC runtime system.
